Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.59,0:40:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi tới để giết anh
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.37,0:40:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.77,0:40:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tại sao...?
